        "body": "## What\r\n\r\nCloses #2\r\n\r\nAdded a GitHub Actions CI workflow that runs automatically on every pull request targeting `dev` and `main`.\r\n\r\n### Changes made\r\n\r\n* Created `.github/workflows/ci.yml`\r\n* Configured the workflow to use Python 3.10\r\n* Enabled pip dependency caching\r\n* Installed project dependencies from `requirements.txt`\r\n* Added automated checks for:\r\n\r\n  * Black\r\n  * isort\r\n  * flake8\r\n  * pytest\r\n\r\n## How to Test\r\n\r\n1. Create a pull request targeting `dev` or `main`.\r\n2. Verify that the GitHub Actions workflow starts automatically.\r\n3. Check that it runs the formatting, linting, and test commands in the expected order.\r\n\r\n## Checklist\r\n\r\n* [x] CI workflow added\r\n* [x] Uses Python 3.10\r\n* [x] Pip dependency caching enabled\r\n* [x] Runs Black, isort, flake8, and pytest\r\n* [x] Tested locally\r\n* [x] Tests pass (`pytest tests/ -v`)\r\n* [x] Code formatted (`black src/ tests/` and `isort src/ tests/`)\r\n* [x] No lint errors (`flake8 src/ tests/`)\r\n* [x] Type hints on all new functions\r\n* [x] Docstrings on all new public functions\r\n* [x] Updated relevant docs if needed\r\n\r\n## Screenshots / Output\r\n\r\nLocal verification completed:\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nblack --check src/ tests/\r\nisort --check src/ tests/\r\nflake8 src/ tests/\r\npytest tests/ -v\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe formatting and lint checks reported existing issues already present in the repository. `pytest` completed successfully with no tests collected.\r\n",
